STATE
v.
Jeremy Daniel RUSSOM 305P16-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 8, 2016. Jeremy D. Russom, Pro Per. Mary Carla Babb, Assistant Attorney General, Robert S. Banks, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 18th of August 2016 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 8th of December 2016."
